{
  "texts": [
    "Phi-3.5-vision, the latest iteration, is a lightweight yet powerful model featuring a 128K token context length and support for both single and multi-image processing.",
    "InternVL The InternVL family includes: Mono-InternVL (Luo et al., 2024a), which established the foundation with its vision-language capabilities; InternVL-2 (Chen et al., 2024c), which expanded the model sizes and improved performance; and InternVL-2.5 (Chen et al., 2025b), the latest iteration that introduces significant architectural and training improvements.",
    "LLaVA LLaVA-1.5 (Liu et al., 2023) uses pretrained CLIP (Radford et al., 2021) and Vi-cuna language model as the backbone, establishing the foundation with impressive performance across 12 benchmark datasets.",
    "LLaVA-OneVision-Qwen2 (Li et al., 2024) pushes performance boundaries across single-image, multi-image, and video scenarios while enabling strong task transfer capabilities.",
    "LLaVA-1.6 (Liu et al., 2024c), or LLaVA-NeXT, further enhances capabilities with increased input resolution, improved visual reasoning, and enhanced OCR capabilities."
  ]
}